|url= http://www.boston.com/lifestyle/articles/2008/04/13/in_rwanda_visionary_doctor_is_moving_mountains_again/?page=2
|title= In Rwanda, visionary doctor is moving mountains again
|author= English, Bella
|date=2008-04-13
|work=The Boston Globe
|accessdate=2008-04-13}}</ref> His younger brother, [[Jeff Farmer (wrestler)|Jeff Farmer]], also known as the nWo Sting, is a well-known athlete, competing on the professional wrestling circuit.<ref name=NewYorker>{{cite web
|accessdate=2007-05-29
